    "body": "Btw, for future reference, this is how you do this in typescript:\r\n\r\n```typescript\r\nfunction callFn<T>(fn: () => T extends Promise<unknown> ? never : T) {\r\n    fn()\r\n}\r\n\r\n// these two compile fine\r\ncallFn(() => {})\r\ncallFn(() => 2)\r\n\r\n// these two don't\r\ncallFn(async () => {})\r\ncallFn(async () => 2)\r\n```",
